@startuml
title Diagrama de Estados - Gestión de Formularios

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
hide empty description

[*] --> CargandoFormulario

state "Cargando Formulario" as CargandoFormulario
state "Formulario Visible" as FormularioVisible
state "Validando Datos" as Validando
state "Guardando Informacion" as Guardando
state "Error de Validacion" as ErrorValidacion
state "Error del Servidor" as ErrorServidor
state "Registro Exitoso" as Exito

CargandoFormulario --> FormularioVisible : Datos listos
FormularioVisible --> Validando : Enviar formulario

Validando --> Guardando : Validacion exitosa
Validando --> ErrorValidacion : Validacion falla

Guardando --> Exito : POST exitoso
Guardando --> ErrorServidor : Error en persistencia

ErrorValidacion --> FormularioVisible : Corregir campos
ErrorServidor --> FormularioVisible : Reintentar

Exito --> [*]

@enduml